{"tid":2040743,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國眾議院議長 pelosi: 美國要用一切可能既工具去回應國安法 （包括經濟制裁）","createTime":"2020-05-28T19:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T02:11:55.000Z","uid":128923,"like":115,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"de7bc243a277de045b4481afc6c3b44ec4cb6ae5","tid":2040743,"uid":128923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T19:36:22.000Z","msg":"要留意既係pelosi 多次為香港人出聲，而且佢係民主黨重要人物之一，可見美國總統選舉鬥黃將無可避免 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後一句亦都畫龍點晴，就美國而言，今次就算經濟利益會捐失都一定要出手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSpeaker Nancy Pelosi issued this statement after Beijing approved moving ahead with a sweeping new &ldquo;national security framework&rdquo; intended to greatly expand its power to suppress speech, including protests, in Hong Kong:   <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The so-called &lsquo;national security framework&rsquo; &ndash; Beijing&rsquo;s latest move against Hong Kong &ndash; threatens the death of the &lsquo;one country, two systems&rsquo; principle.  This excessive law brazenly accelerates Beijing&rsquo;s years-long assault on Hong Kong&rsquo;s political and economic freedoms, coming after the threat of the extradition bill and of police brutality last fall.  All freedom-loving people must come together to condemn this law.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;In the U.S. Congress, there has always been bipartisan support for freedom, justice and real autonomy for the people of Hong Kong, and we were proud to pass the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act.   Per the law, the Secretary of State has certified that Hong Kong no longer continues to warrant the special relationship it has enjoyed.  <span style=\"color: red;\">The next step is now for the Administration to work with Congress on an appropriate response.  We must consider all tools available, including visa limitations and economic penalties.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;If America does not speak out for human rights in China because of commercial interests, we lose all moral authority to speak out elsewhere.&quot;</span>  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.speaker.gov/newsroom/52820-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speaker.gov%2Fnewsroom%2F52820-1&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=77dd9f80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.speaker.gov/newsroom/52820-1</a>"},{"pid":"416046900a5c004d17d434352cca279b6dc5ebcc","tid":2040743,"uid":128923,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T19:36:48.000Z","msg":"入去多謝人啦：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpeakerPelosi/status/1266085194777464833\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSpeakerPelosi%2Fstatus%2F1266085194777464833&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=da916131\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSpeakerPelosi%2Fstatus%2F1266085194777464833&h=544394b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SpeakerPelosi/status/1266085194777464833</a>"},{"pid":"4d226d6b2b883f518ecd95ec1f416efff674a2db","tid":2040743,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T19:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0030b36168a389275494f8f07e64bb7000f4049","tid":2040743,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T19:46:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fd3962910a67d87b3c83bed6809ef2cd80bd8b43","tid":2040743,"uid":128923,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T19:47:50.000Z","msg":"btw trump 聽日都開記者會講中國 <br />\n睇黎聽日係大審判日<br />\n如果trump 制裁力度唔夠 應該會瘋狂比民主黨背刺<br />\n所以應該.... OK 既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please